  "detailed_description": "<h1>⭐️CARDS AND BADGES⭐️</h1><p><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1615060/extras/ed624856df046be0064d606757dce79c.avif?t=1761592488\" width=600 height=158 /></span></p><br><h1>About the Game</h1><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1615060/extras/64dddb5e9f37d49f29fb0033c412ba6f.avif?t=1761592488\" width=605 height=157 /></span><br>The girls are very hungry, feed them, they are waiting for you.<br>Yummy Girl is a puzzle game, in which all you need is to swop bricks, in order to make the pictures restored.<br><br>Easy win:<br>Keyboard Сtrl+D - Complete Level<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1615060/extras/f0a448c23e95da5b8629dca63201a7aa.poster.avif?t=1761592488\" width=600 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1615060/extras/f0a448c23e95da5b8629dca63201a7aa.webm?t=1761592488\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1615060/extras/f0a448c23e95da5b8629dca63201a7aa.mp4?t=1761592488\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1615060/extras/cfb1d4c7d29f4c65a13e2a4afefdecf0.avif?t=1761592488\" width=605 height=400 /></span><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\">Game Feature:</ul><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Artworks<br></li><li>12 cute girls<br></li><li>Relaxing music</li></ul>",
